snippet.title: Hotel Magnate - Trailer
snippet.description:
Hotel Magnate is a Tycoon/Simulator Game where the player creates and builds their own hotel, motel or resort. Overcome the challenges of running a hotel and see your dream destination come to life

Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/832360/

Grand Opening Coming Soon!

Website: http://hotel-magnate.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheHotelMagnate
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hotelmagnate/
